## Why This Is Asked

Tests ability to apply multi-tenant isolation, data governance, and IR planning in a Databricks context beyond generic concepts.

## Key Concepts

- Unity Catalog RBAC and object-level permissions
- Tenant-scoped secret scopes and secret management
- Dynamic data masking and access controls for notebooks
- Audit logs and SIEM integration for detection
- Incident response playbooks and metrics

## Code Example

